'Following a scan it was found he had injuries to his liver, eye and had internal bleeding.

'He was transferred to Leeds General Infirmary for further treatment, where he remains in a poorly condition this evening.

'This was a terrible accident which has resulted in a small child suffering serious injuries. Police are not treating this incident as suspicious and our thoughts are with his family.'

